text: Yeah, I think it was mostly the brim that was sticking out. It could also be that the dimension of the web slicer is a little bit off compared to the actual size. If you want to make sure next time, I recommend downloading PrusaSlicer on your computer, slice your stl file locally, and upload the GCode to Octoprint directly. feel free to reach out to me if you have further questions about that
